org.orgName: District Court of the Third Judicial District of Washington Territory

body.p: Office of the Sheriff of King County } ss Washington Territory

I hereby certify that I served the writ of Habeas Corpus of which the annexed is a true copy, on the 10th day of May 1888 and personally served the same on John Coldwell constable of King County, on the 10th day of May 1888 by delivering to and leaving with him personally in King County said original writ of Habeas Corpus.
Dated on Seattle W.T. on this 10th day of May 1888 William Cochrane Sheriff of King County W.T. By. W.B. Thompson Deputy
Sheriffs Fees Serving Writ 1.00 Copy of Writ .40 Travel .20 Return .50 $2.10
